{"tid":788199,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭北京抵制　帕勞總統：發展「重質不重量」旅遊業　指不認同「一中」　較認同台灣民主價值","createTime":"2018-08-21T09:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T10:18:22.000Z","uid":53379,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bfb6899d0b810689e5d9eb9e8122caeaec799455","tid":788199,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遭北京抵制　帕勞總統：發展「重質不重量」旅遊業　指不認同「一中」　較認同台灣民主價值</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180820/s00004/59915902b6d34d3ec533af13f3066626.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180820%2Fs00004%2F59915902b6d34d3ec533af13f3066626.jpg&h=054abd1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩岸外交戰持續，有傳中國大陸去年11月以太平洋島國帕勞與台灣維持外交關係為由，下令旅行社停售飛帕勞航班，令中國大陸觀光客銳減，迫使帕勞今年7月宣布將停飛中國大陸航線。帕勞總統雷門格紹近日（Tommy Remengesau Jr.）接受路透社訪問時，就強調他們政府的民主價值觀與台灣相近，未來希望發展「重質不重量」的旅遊業模式。<br />\n<br />\n雷門格紹指，雖然現時未收到過任何官方禁令，但北京希望迫使他們與台灣斷交並非秘密。他明言帕勞不認同「一中」政策，強調雖然歡迎中國大陸投資，但現時他們政府相對認同台灣的民主價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，帕勞過往招待過多旅客，導致生態環境受損，直言數量並不能為帕勞帶來可觀收入，故現時當局正決心發展「重質不重量」的旅遊業。<br />\n<br />\n然而，受中國客銳減影響，帕勞旅遊業轉型道路似乎仍非常漫長。帕勞航空與帕勞一所主要酒店早前表示，7至8月的航班或住房都無預訂。另外，路透社記者在最大城市科羅爾採訪期間，發現當地旅行社十室九空，旅遊巴閒置在停車場。<br />\n<br />\n為協助當地慘淡的旅遊業，台外交部6月起表示會每周增加開兩個飛帕勞航班，為期兩個月。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180820/s00004/1534742119015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180820%2Fs00004%2F1534742119015&d=eLc2k4X4fye4VeyyALA54JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=14ac9c8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180820%2Fs00004%2F1534742119015&h=eb468318\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180820/s00004/1534742119015</a>"},{"pid":"d97f5c571852dd631ce43f4a296e541c7e7a996c","tid":788199,"uid":19557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T09:38:35.000Z","msg":"有d 想去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401c3482763ed3c3a60f2478ad98247a8231daa0","tid":788199,"uid":1672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T09:45:10.000Z","msg":"寒天飲雪水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f1f8ab8484833ac62e66550645da15752c5e10","tid":788199,"uid":9887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T09:46:43.000Z","msg":"一search帛琉/palau<br />\n全部都係講支那依單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7487e14e783b91fbdd37c459f371233d9dffdc1b","tid":788199,"uid":686,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d97f5c571852dd631ce43f4a296e541c7e7a996c","tid":788199,"uid":19557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T09:38:35.000Z","msg":"有d 想去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T10:18:22.000Z","msg":"取消咗個航班就係飛香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}